3
00:01:20,500 --> 00:01:26,240
海蒂和爷爷

4
00:01:26,250 --> 00:01:28,660
海蒂！过来！
Heidi! Come on!

5
00:01:50,580 --> 00:01:51,580
你好，迪提
Hello, Dete.

6
00:01:57,200 --> 00:01:58,790
好热
I'm hot.

7
00:02:00,370 --> 00:02:03,240
- 还有多远？ - 海蒂，就在山顶
- Is it far?  - Heidi, it's right at the top.

8
00:02:04,250 --> 00:02:05,660
你好，迪提
Hello, Dete.

9
00:02:05,830 --> 00:02:07,040
你好
Hello.

10
00:02:08,830 --> 00:02:12,120
- 这是你妹妹的女儿？ - 是的
- Is that your late sister's daughter?  - Yes.

11
00:02:12,290 --> 00:02:15,200
- 过来，海蒂，我们要走了  - 她都长这么大了
- Come on, Heidi. We have to go.  - She's got so big.

12
00:02:18,080 --> 00:02:19,870
过来
Come on.

13
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:25,040
你要带她去哪？
Where are you taking her?

14
00:02:27,080 --> 00:02:30,240
- 到她爷爷那去  - 去阿蒙治叔叔那？
- To her grandfather.  - To the Alp-Uncle?

15
00:02:30,410 --> 00:02:31,830
我的老天！
Good heavens!

16
00:02:32,120 --> 00:02:33,790
迪提
Dete.

17
00:02:33,950 --> 00:02:36,870
他很冷漠讨厌与人接触
He's godless and hates every living soul.

18
00:02:37,040 --> 00:02:39,080
据说他甚至忘记了怎么说话
They say he even forgot how to speak.

19
00:02:39,250 --> 00:02:41,790
我要把她寄养在别人家？
Am I meant to put her in a home?

20
00:02:42,080 --> 00:02:44,620
或者把她交给我们不认识的农民家？
Or give her to some farmer we don't know?

21
00:02:45,870 --> 00:02:49,240
你应当明白没有人想多养活一个人
You know that nobody wants an extra mouth to feed.

22
00:02:50,120 --> 00:02:53,240
同陌生人呆在一起也许对她比较好
She might have been better off with strangers.

23
00:02:53,410 --> 00:02:57,950
他甚至与自己的儿子闹翻了，愿上帝宽恕他的灵魂
He even fell out with his own son. May God rest his soul.

24
00:02:58,250 --> 00:03:01,950
同时我确定他不会想和这个孩子扯上关系
And I'm sure he won't want anything to do with the child.

25
00:03:18,040 --> 00:03:21,080
海蒂！你在哪？
Heidi! Where are you?

26
00:03:22,330 --> 00:03:25,450
海蒂，马上过来
Heidi, come here right now!

27
00:03:28,290 --> 00:03:30,160
过来！
Coming!

28
00:04:14,910 --> 00:04:16,200
你好，爷爷
Hello, Grandfather.

29
00:04:20,660 --> 00:04:22,790
你好，阿蒙治叔叔
Hello, Alp-Uncle.

30
00:04:24,910 --> 00:04:26,660
她叫海蒂
This is Heidi.

31
00:04:27,750 --> 00:04:28,870
你的孙女
Your grandchild.

32
00:04:35,750 --> 00:04:38,370
我在法兰克福找到份工作
I've found a position in Frankfurt.

33
00:04:38,910 --> 00:04:42,450
所以我把她带给你
So now I'm bringing her to you.

34
00:04:43,620 --> 00:04:45,870
她毕竟流淌着你的血脉
She's your own flesh and blood after all.

35
00:04:46,160 --> 00:04:48,040
带着她滚
Go! And take her with you.

36
00:04:49,580 --> 00:04:52,490
我已经照顾她五年了
I've looked after her for five years.

37
00:04:52,790 --> 00:04:55,540
- 现在没法照顾了  - 滚！
- But I can't do it anymore.  - Get out of here!

38
00:05:05,040 --> 00:05:08,120
海蒂，听好了
Heidi, listen to me.

39
00:05:08,290 --> 00:05:10,540
没有什么好害怕的
There's nothing to be scared of.

40
00:05:10,700 --> 00:05:14,290
我确定你爷爷不会伤害你
I'm sure Uncle won't hurt you.

41
00:05:17,950 --> 00:05:19,700
好的，过去吧
Right, now go.

42
00:05:23,000 --> 00:05:24,620
去啊！
Go!

43
00:05:25,620 --> 00:05:27,370
上帝原谅我吧
God forgive me.

44
00:05:40,830 --> 00:05:44,200
孩子！把这孩子带走！
The child!Take the child with you!

45
00:05:46,790 --> 00:05:48,790
过来，跟她走！
Go on, go with her!

46
00:05:50,200 --> 00:05:52,580
她不要我了
But she doesn't want me either.

47
00:06:10,700 --> 00:06:19,490
爷爷？
Grandfather?

48
00:08:03,370 --> 00:08:05,700
早上好，爷爷
Good morning, Grandfather.

49
00:08:38,580 --> 00:08:40,200
喝吧
Drink.

50
00:09:03,580 --> 00:09:06,160
- 谢谢  - 我带你去牧师那一趟
- Thank you.  - I'll take you to the parson.

51
00:09:06,330 --> 00:09:08,540
他会知道怎么处理你
He'll know what to do with you.

52
00:09:22,450 --> 00:09:24,200
张嘴
Open up.

53
00:09:29,620 --> 00:09:31,580
孩子很结实
The child is strong.

54
00:09:33,250 --> 00:09:35,040
健康
And healthy.

55
00:09:35,200 --> 00:09:36,870
她不会有问题的
She won't be much trouble.

56
00:09:37,040 --> 00:09:38,870
她不能和我呆在一起
She can't stay with me.

57
00:09:42,410 --> 00:09:44,290
好吧
Okay, fine.

58
00:09:44,950 --> 00:09:48,830
- 这几天我要去迈恩费尔德一趟  - 也许有人可以收留她
- I'm going to Maienfeld in three days.  - Maybe a farmer has a use for her.

59
00:09:49,870 --> 00:09:51,700
毕竟，是个家
Otherwise, it's a home.

60
00:09:52,580 --> 00:09:54,790
但是她这段时间得和你住在一起
But she has to stay with you until then.

61
00:09:55,790 --> 00:09:58,040
到时我带她过来
I'll bring her down then.

62
00:09:59,160 --> 00:10:02,160
照顾你的孙女是你应尽的责任
It's your Christian duty to look after your grandchild.

63
00:10:09,250 --> 00:10:11,540
好了，下来吧
Here, off you go.

64
00:10:23,750 --> 00:10:25,240
爷爷？
Grandfather?

65
00:10:26,330 --> 00:10:29,080
今晚我还睡在畜棚里吗？
Should I sleep in the stable again tonight?

66
00:10:30,330 --> 00:10:32,120
随你睡哪儿
Sleep wherever you want.

67
00:10:46,540 --> 00:10:48,410
你只有一把椅子
You only have one chair.

68
00:10:52,830 --> 00:10:54,620
一张床
And only one bed.

69
00:11:02,000 --> 00:11:03,910
上面是干什么的
What's that up there?

70
00:11:22,000 --> 00:11:25,490
我想睡在上面的干草里，可以吗？
I want to sleep up here in the hay.Am I allowed?

71
00:11:29,080 --> 00:11:30,740
爷爷？
Grandfather?

72
00:11:32,580 --> 00:11:34,240
我不想去别人家
I'd rather not go into a home.

73
00:12:18,830 --> 00:12:21,740
- 早上好，爷爷  - 喝你的牛奶
- Good morning, Grandfather.  - Drink your milk.

74
00:12:31,750 --> 00:12:33,740
停下！
Stop there!  -

75
00:12:38,580 --> 00:12:40,490
早上好，山羊们
Good morning, goats.  -

76
00:12:41,330 --> 00:12:43,160
小熊、小天鹅[羊名]，过来！
Little Bear! Little Swan! Come on!

77
00:12:45,410 --> 00:12:47,540
来吧
Come on! Chop chop!

78
00:12:47,830 --> 00:12:50,620
早上好，牧羊人
Good day, General Goatherd.

79
00:12:54,950 --> 00:12:57,950
今天带女孩和你一起去阿尔卑斯山上去
Take the girl with you out on the alp today.

80
00:13:00,000 --> 00:13:02,700
她不知道山上的事情
She doesn't know how things work in the mountains.

81
00:13:03,950 --> 00:13:05,740
你好，我叫海蒂
Hello. My name is Heidi.

82
00:13:09,830 --> 00:13:12,580
- 好吧  - 谢谢
- Right.  - Thank you.

83
00:13:13,250 --> 00:13:14,790
过来
Come on.

84
00:13:19,500 --> 00:13:22,450
听到他说的了吗？你得听我的话
Did you hear him?You have to do what I say.

85
00:13:22,620 --> 00:13:23,830
好的
Yeah, yeah.

86
00:13:24,290 --> 00:13:26,990
- 你叫什么名字？ - 皮特
- What's your name?  - Peter.

87
00:13:27,160 --> 00:13:30,240
- 你和他一起住吗？ - 是的，他是我爷爷
- Are you living with him now?  - Yes, he's my grandfather.

88
00:13:30,410 --> 00:13:31,910
你爷爷？
Your grandfather?

89
00:13:32,500 --> 00:13:34,790
为什么不和你的父母一起住
Why don't you live with your parents?

90
00:13:34,950 --> 00:13:36,790
他们去世了
Because they're dead.

91
00:13:38,080 --> 00:13:40,240
我父亲也去世了
My father is dead too.

92
00:13:40,950 --> 00:13:44,120
以前我和我的姑姑迪提一起住在拉格斯
I was living with my Aunt Dete in Bad Ragaz until now.

93
00:13:44,290 --> 00:13:46,700
一整天我都得坐在家里
I had to sit inside all day.

94
00:13:46,870 --> 00:13:49,040
这里太好了，我可以出来玩！
But here is much better.I can be outside!

95
00:13:49,330 --> 00:13:52,080
- 跟紧我  - 好的
- Hey, stay with me!  - Yeah, yeah.

96
00:14:40,580 --> 00:14:42,160
那个小的叫什么？
What's that little one called?

97
00:14:43,200 --> 00:14:47,410
- Snowhopper  - 你能教我怎么生火吗？
- Snowhopper.  - Will you show me how to make a fire?

98
00:14:48,830 --> 00:14:50,330
当然可以
Sure.

99
00:14:54,910 --> 00:14:56,200
嘿！皮特
Hey, Peter.

100
00:14:57,080 --> 00:14:59,450
你吃了我的奶酪和香肠吗？
Did you eat some of my cheese and sausage?

101
00:14:59,620 --> 00:15:00,700
什么，我吗？
What, me?

102
00:15:01,500 --> 00:15:03,580
不，不是我
No, that wasn't me.

103
00:15:04,410 --> 00:15:05,910
还能是谁？
Who else could it have been?

104
00:15:06,410 --> 00:15:09,080
不知道，也许是山羊干的？
I don't know. Maybe a goat?

105
00:15:10,000 --> 00:15:11,040
山羊？
A goat?

106
00:15:14,370 --> 00:15:15,580
停下！
Hey! Stay there.

107
00:15:16,370 --> 00:15:19,950
小天鹅，停下
Little Swan, Thistlefinch! Stop it, stop!

108
00:15:22,000 --> 00:15:24,660
走开，停止打斗
Get away! Stop that!

109
00:15:24,950 --> 00:15:27,580
- 待在那里  - 放过他
- Just you wait!  - Leave him!

110
00:15:27,750 --> 00:15:30,200
没听见吗，我让你待在那里
Do you never listen?I said stay over there!

111
00:15:30,500 --> 00:15:32,790
不要打它，它们不打架了
Stop hitting them!They stopped fighting.

112
00:15:32,950 --> 00:15:36,290
需要惩罚它们，因为打架导致产奶少了
They need to be punished.They give less milk if they fight.

113
00:15:36,580 --> 00:15:40,290
如果你不打它们，我分一半吃的给你
If you stop hitting them,I'll give you half my food.

114
00:15:40,450 --> 00:15:41,490
一半？
Half of it?

115
00:15:44,450 --> 00:15:45,490
每天？
Every day?

116
00:15:45,790 --> 00:15:48,870
但你不能再打这些山羊
But you're not allowed to hit the goats anymore.

117
00:15:49,040 --> 00:15:51,040
成交？
Do you promise?

118
00:15:51,330 --> 00:15:53,540
每天，一半
Every day. Half.

119
00:16:02,750 --> 00:16:07,160
- 看到了吗？ - 看到了
- Do you see? Look.  - I can see.

120
00:16:08,000 --> 00:16:10,040
看，快，趴下
Look. Ouick, get down!

121
00:16:10,200 --> 00:16:11,370
该你了
Now your turn.

122
00:16:11,660 --> 00:16:13,040
- 我  - 是的
- Me?  - Yes.

123
00:16:36,830 --> 00:16:38,660
- 海蒂？ - 嗯？
- Heidi?  - Yes?

124
00:16:38,950 --> 00:16:43,200
- 不要提食物的事情  - 我不会说的
- Maybe don't mention the food.  - I won't say anything.

125
00:16:44,950 --> 00:16:49,160
村里人说他杀过人
In the village they say he killed someone once.

126
00:17:09,080 --> 00:17:11,080
谢谢
Thank you.

127
00:17:11,700 --> 00:17:14,370
我还是睡在畜棚里吧
I'd rather sleep in the stable affer all.

128
00:17:16,790 --> 00:17:19,990
皮特和你讲了我的传闻吗？
Did Peter tell you stories about me?

129
00:17:24,620 --> 00:17:26,080
你相信他的话？
And you just believe him?

130
00:17:27,870 --> 00:17:30,290
他说的是真的吗？
Is it true what he says?

131
00:17:30,870 --> 00:17:33,740
人们喜欢说些鸡毛蒜皮的事情
People like saying nasty things.

132
00:17:35,200 --> 00:17:39,450
你需要决定相信自己的眼睛和耳朵
You have to decide whether to trust your own eyes and ears

133
00:17:39,620 --> 00:17:41,700
还是别人的话
or what other people say.

134
00:18:07,200 --> 00:18:09,830
晚安，爷爷
Goodnight, Grandfather.

135
00:18:44,410 --> 00:18:46,370
好美
Lovely.

136
00:18:48,910 --> 00:18:51,080
我对这里很熟
I know my way around up here.

137
00:19:23,120 --> 00:19:25,740
明天我告诉你雪绒花长在哪
I'll show you tomorrow where the edelweiss grows.

138
00:19:28,290 --> 00:19:29,660
皮特
Peter.

139
00:19:31,540 --> 00:19:35,370
明天我得走了，爷爷要带我去牧师那里
I'll be gone tomorrow.Grandfather is taking me to the parson.

140
00:19:35,660 --> 00:19:36,740
什么？
What?

141
00:19:38,500 --> 00:19:41,080
[其实是舍不得那些吃的了吧！…^_^]
我又要独自和这些愚蠢的山羊呆在一起了
I'm on my own with these stupid goats again.

142
00:19:43,160 --> 00:19:45,830
走开
Shoo! Move! Come on.

143
00:19:46,120 --> 00:19:47,910
走开
Go! Move it!

144
00:20:13,080 --> 00:20:15,290
看你弄成什么样了
What on earth do you look like?

145
00:20:17,910 --> 00:20:19,740
爷爷？
Grandfather?

146
00:20:21,500 --> 00:20:23,870
这是我的椅子？
Is the chair for me?

147
00:20:24,040 --> 00:20:25,580
还能是谁的
Who else?

148
00:20:29,330 --> 00:20:31,120
但我明天要离开了啊
But I'm leaving tomorrow.

149
00:20:32,120 --> 00:20:34,240
你明天要去山上
You're going out on the alp tomorrow.

150
00:20:35,120 --> 00:20:37,040
后天也去？
And the next day too?

151
00:20:37,200 --> 00:20:38,330
当然
Certainly.

152
00:20:40,000 --> 00:20:42,910
不要再问问题了，去洗干净你的脸
Don't ask so many questions and go and wash your face.

153
00:20:47,120 --> 00:20:49,830
谢谢，谢谢，太感谢你了
Thank you, thank you, thank you!

154
00:20:52,290 --> 00:20:56,160
皮特，我能留下来了
Peter! I'm allowed to stay!

155
00:21:48,080 --> 00:21:51,200
- 今天是我最后一天来了  - 为什么
- Today is the last day I'll be here.  - Why?

156
00:21:51,370 --> 00:21:52,910
我得去上学
I have to go to school.

157
00:21:53,080 --> 00:21:54,790
什么时候回来？
When are you coming back?

158
00:21:56,080 --> 00:21:57,490
春天吧，我想
In the spring, I think.

159
00:21:58,120 --> 00:22:00,040
直到春天？
Not until the spring?

160
00:22:07,200 --> 00:22:08,660
你可以下山到我家来
You can come down and visit.

161
00:22:09,450 --> 00:22:11,540
我奶奶会很高兴看见你
Grandmother will be pleased to see you.

162
00:22:17,750 --> 00:22:20,330
别吃了，吃的够多了
No more eating, you've had enough!

163
00:22:23,950 --> 00:22:25,660
跟上！
Come on!

164
00:22:28,410 --> 00:22:30,160
我能去上学吗？
May I go to school too?

165
00:22:31,540 --> 00:22:32,580
过来，吃饭
Come on, eat.

166
00:22:38,040 --> 00:22:39,290
看谁来了
Look who's there.

167
00:22:40,080 --> 00:22:43,200
难以置信
That's unbelievable.

168
00:22:45,330 --> 00:22:48,200
他不应该被允许照顾孩子
He shouldn't be allowed to take care of a child.

169
00:22:48,500 --> 00:22:50,740
他看过来啦
He's looking over.

170
00:23:17,750 --> 00:23:19,120
早上好
Good day.

171
00:23:19,950 --> 00:23:21,240
你好
Hello.

172
00:23:22,120 --> 00:23:23,330
阿蒙治叔叔…
Alp-Uncle...

173
00:23:24,410 --> 00:23:26,910
对这个女孩你有什么规划
What do you have planned for the girl?

174
00:23:27,080 --> 00:23:28,950
和你没关系
That's nothing to do with you.

175
00:23:29,250 --> 00:23:31,660
她应该去上学
In a year she'll have to go to school.

176
00:23:31,830 --> 00:23:34,370
她不需要
She doesn't have to do anything.

177
00:23:34,540 --> 00:23:37,740
讲点理，每个孩子都该读书
Be sensible.Every child must learn to read.

178
00:23:38,040 --> 00:23:41,620
她没法在冬天里独自一人从山上下来
She can't come down from the alp on her own in the winter.

179
00:23:41,790 --> 00:23:44,370
过来，孩子，出去玩
Come on, child.You go outside.

180
00:23:48,750 --> 00:23:51,290
整个冬天独自一人呆在山上
Alone the whole winter,up on that alp.

181
00:23:51,580 --> 00:23:55,450
- 这么大的孩子需要朋友  - 她应有尽有
- A child of that age needs friends.  - She has all she needs.

182
00:23:58,290 --> 00:23:59,790
这是违法的
It's against the law.

183
00:24:01,080 --> 00:24:04,370
对你的法律不感兴趣
I'm not interested in your laws.

184
00:24:14,450 --> 00:24:15,620
过来
Come on.

185
00:24:18,290 --> 00:24:20,490
老顽固
Such a pig-headed fellow.

186
00:24:33,540 --> 00:24:35,790
看
Here, look.

187
00:24:37,450 --> 00:24:39,330
做好了
It's finished.

188
00:24:42,580 --> 00:24:43,950
好漂亮
Beautiful.

189
00:24:45,080 --> 00:24:46,330
谢谢你，爷爷
Thank you, Grandfather.

190
00:24:52,330 --> 00:24:54,910
要是春天来了就好了
If only it were spring again.

191
00:25:30,540 --> 00:25:39,080
快
Faster!

192
00:25:59,660 --> 00:26:01,490
谢谢
Thank you.

193
00:26:01,660 --> 00:26:04,870
天黑后我会来接你
When it gets dark,I'll come and pick you up.

194
00:26:11,410 --> 00:26:13,040
皮特在家吗？
Hello, is Peter there?

195
00:26:13,200 --> 00:26:15,910
他在学校，进来吧
He's at school.But come inside.

196
00:26:23,290 --> 00:26:25,740
母亲，我们有客人来了，是海蒂
Mother, we have a visitor.It's Heidi.

197
00:26:26,450 --> 00:26:27,830
你好
Hello.

198
00:26:28,000 --> 00:26:30,490
孩子，她看不见
Child, she can't see.

199
00:26:31,790 --> 00:26:34,950
靠近点，海蒂
Come a little closer, Heidi.

200
00:26:37,870 --> 00:26:40,370
奶奶，你什么都看不见吗？
Can you see nothing, Grandmother?

201
00:26:40,660 --> 00:26:42,740
是看不见
With my eyes, nothing at all.

202
00:26:42,910 --> 00:26:45,240
但可以用手感受世界
But with my hands,it's different.

203
00:26:48,910 --> 00:26:51,120
- 海蒂  - 皮特
- Heidi!  - Peter!

204
00:26:56,500 --> 00:26:57,540
谢谢
Thank you.

205
00:26:57,700 --> 00:27:00,450
你什么也没错过，学校好无聊
You're not missing anything.School is so boring.

206
00:27:00,620 --> 00:27:03,040
你这样说是因为你不会读书
You just say that because you still can't read.

207
00:27:03,200 --> 00:27:06,620
你也不会，读书有什么好的
You can't either.What good does reading do up here?

208
00:27:06,910 --> 00:27:07,950
吃你的饭
Eat your food!

209
00:27:12,620 --> 00:27:15,160
奶奶，吃我的吧
You can have mine, Grandmother.

210
00:27:15,330 --> 00:27:18,330
谢谢，海蒂，它太硬了
Thank you, Heidi,but it's too hard.

211
00:27:19,450 --> 00:27:22,160
我快没牙了
I hardly have any teeth left, you know.

212
00:27:23,250 --> 00:27:24,370
那我给我吧
Then I'll take it.

213
00:27:34,910 --> 00:27:38,240
奶奶看不见，你知道吗？
Grandmother can't see.Did you know?

214
00:27:39,450 --> 00:27:42,410
她也不能吃陈面包
And she can't eat any stale bread at all.

215
00:27:45,200 --> 00:27:49,620
我们很幸运，不是吗，爷爷
We're lucky, aren't we Grandfather?

216
00:28:41,620 --> 00:28:43,700
噢，那里
Whoa there!

217
00:28:57,910 --> 00:29:00,330
叔叔？你好
Uncle? Hello.

218
00:29:02,080 --> 00:29:04,200
我带来一些好消息
I've got some good news.

219
00:29:05,290 --> 00:29:07,790
我帮海蒂找到了好人家
I've found a place for Heidi,

220
00:29:07,950 --> 00:29:10,660
在法兰克福，我雇主的朋友家里
with friends of my employers,in Frankfurt.

221
00:29:15,660 --> 00:29:17,790
这是一个受人尊敬的家庭
It's a well-respected family,

222
00:29:17,950 --> 00:29:23,580
海蒂可以和她们的女儿一起去上学
and Heidi could even go to school with their young daughter.

223
00:29:24,750 --> 00:29:26,540
对她来说太好了
It's a wonderful chance for her.

224
00:29:27,580 --> 00:29:29,540
说句话吧
Say something at least!

225
00:29:30,330 --> 00:29:32,870
说完了就滚
When you're finished, you can go.

226
00:29:33,500 --> 00:29:34,910
我想带走她
But I want to take her with me.

227
00:29:35,200 --> 00:29:36,700
海蒂待在这里
Heidi is staying here.

228
00:29:40,450 --> 00:29:43,620
村里人说你不让她上学
In the village they sayyou don't let her go to school.

229
00:29:44,750 --> 00:29:48,490
因为你的固执她不会读也不会写
Because of your obstinacy,she won't learn to read or write!

230
00:29:48,660 --> 00:29:50,490
你想让她在这里粗野下去？
You want her to turn wild up here?

231
00:29:50,790 --> 00:29:53,910
你为什么突然这么关心她？
Why do you care about her all of a sudden?

232
00:29:54,080 --> 00:29:57,620
叔叔，上次我也没办法
Uncle, last time I had no other choice.

233
00:29:57,910 --> 00:30:00,290
没什么好说的了
There's nothing more to say.

234
00:30:03,250 --> 00:30:05,620
如果你不让她上学
If you don't let her go to school,

235
00:30:05,910 --> 00:30:09,160
他们会带走她并把她送到别人家里
they'll take her away from you and put her in a home.

236
00:30:09,790 --> 00:30:13,290
我今天要带走她，如果需要的话会寻求村民的帮助
I'm taking her today. With help from the villagers, if needs be.

237
00:30:14,250 --> 00:30:15,870
孩子在哪？
Where is the child?

238
00:30:17,620 --> 00:30:19,290
海蒂是我的
Heidi is mine.

239
00:30:19,450 --> 00:30:21,040
现在滚！
Now get out of here.

240
00:30:47,580 --> 00:30:49,910
- 海蒂  - 迪提？
- Heidi!  - Dete?

241
00:30:50,790 --> 00:30:52,990
- 迪提姑姑  - 海蒂，我的孩子
- Aunt Dete!  - Heidi, my child.

242
00:30:53,290 --> 00:30:54,330
过来
Come here.

243
00:30:55,830 --> 00:30:57,620
想我吗？
Have you missed me lots?

244
00:30:58,660 --> 00:31:01,240
小孩，放你的羊去
Boy, go back to your goats.

245
00:31:01,410 --> 00:31:04,950
我和海蒂有话要说
I have to talk to Heidi.Come on.

246
00:31:07,120 --> 00:31:08,450
坐下
Sit down.

247
00:31:13,500 --> 00:31:14,700
听我说
Listen to me.

248
00:31:14,870 --> 00:31:19,290
你想住在一个又大又漂亮的房子里吗？
How would you like to live in a big, beautiful house?

249
00:31:20,660 --> 00:31:23,950
泽塞曼一家，来自法兰克福的非常好的人
The Sesemanns,very kind people from Frankfurt,

250
00:31:24,120 --> 00:31:26,740
正在为他们的女儿寻找朋友
are looking for a friend for their daughter.

251
00:31:28,160 --> 00:31:29,620
但我喜欢这里
But I like it here.

252
00:31:31,080 --> 00:31:34,990
但是法兰克福的女孩期待你的到来
But the girl in Frankfurt is so looking forward to you coming.

253
00:31:35,700 --> 00:31:37,450
我还是想和爷爷待在一起
I'd rather stay with Grandfather.

254
00:31:37,750 --> 00:31:41,830
海蒂，爷爷让你和我一起走
Heidi, Grandfather wants you to come with me.

255
00:31:44,080 --> 00:31:45,120
真的？
Really?

256
00:31:46,950 --> 00:31:50,080
孩子，我们都希望把最好的给你
Child, we both just want what is best for you.

257
00:31:52,330 --> 00:31:54,790
过来，火车快要开了
Come along.The train is leaving soon.

258
00:31:54,950 --> 00:31:58,330
- 但我得说再见  - 没时间了
- But I have to say goodbye.  - We don't have any time.

259
00:31:58,500 --> 00:32:00,790
- 远吗？ - 不远
- Is it far away?  - No, no.

260
00:32:00,950 --> 00:32:03,080
如果我不喜欢那里呢
And what if I don't like it?

261
00:32:03,910 --> 00:32:05,620
你可以回来
Then you can come back home.

262
00:32:05,790 --> 00:32:07,790
我保证
I promise.

263
00:32:07,950 --> 00:32:09,410
跟上
Come on.

264
00:32:20,000 --> 00:32:23,240
过来，快点
Come on, hurry!

265
00:32:27,700 --> 00:32:29,040
海蒂在哪
Where is Heidi?

266
00:32:42,250 --> 00:32:43,740
快点
Go, hurry!

267
00:32:49,500 --> 00:32:51,080
上来
Hop on.

268
00:32:52,200 --> 00:32:54,120
- 出发吧  - 好的
- Off we go!  - All right.

269
00:33:09,660 --> 00:33:12,540
他们走了，你又晚了，不是吗？
They've gone!You're late again, aren't you?

270
00:33:19,250 --> 00:33:21,410
一直在寻找
Keep looking.

271
00:33:30,910 --> 00:33:33,790
孩子还活着真是一个奇迹
It's a miracle the child is still alive.

272
00:34:14,950 --> 00:34:16,200
海蒂，待在这
Heidi, stay here.

273
00:34:16,700 --> 00:34:18,330
待在这
Stay here!

274
00:34:39,200 --> 00:34:42,790
海蒂，和我来，跟上
Heidi, come with me.Come inside.

275
00:35:08,120 --> 00:35:09,160
有空吗
Are you free?

276
00:35:10,040 --> 00:35:12,160
请去泽塞曼家
The Sesemann mansion, please.

277
00:35:13,450 --> 00:35:14,870
过来
Come on.

278
00:35:39,750 --> 00:35:41,410
海蒂
Heidi!

279
00:35:52,500 --> 00:35:53,950
出来
Get out.

280
00:36:02,910 --> 00:36:05,040
- 日安，女士  - 日安
- Good day, ladies.  - Good day.

281
00:36:08,830 --> 00:36:09,910
欢迎，女士
Welcome, ladies.

282
00:36:11,040 --> 00:36:13,740
洛特梅尔小姐正在等我们
Miss Rottenmeier is waiting for us.

283
00:36:14,870 --> 00:36:16,490
请跟着我
Please follow me.

284
00:36:46,330 --> 00:36:47,950
海蒂，住手
Heidi, stop it!

285
00:36:48,660 --> 00:36:51,990
现在我要向洛特梅尔小姐介绍你，好吗？
I'm introducing you to Miss Rottenmeier now, okay?

286
00:36:52,160 --> 00:36:54,540
她是年轻小姐的家庭教师
That's the young lady's governess.

287
00:36:54,700 --> 00:36:55,740
家庭教师？
Governess?

288
00:36:55,910 --> 00:37:01,160
她是一位非常优秀的女士，现在照顾克拉拉小姐
She's a very distinguished woman who looks affer Miss Klara.

289
00:37:01,330 --> 00:37:03,040
好好表现
So behave yourself!

290
00:37:03,200 --> 00:37:06,790
- 洛特梅尔小姐等着见你们  - 好的，跟上
- Miss Rottenmeier will see you now.  - Right. Come along.

291
00:37:18,080 --> 00:37:21,450
不幸的是，我没时间给她换衣服
Unfortunately, I had no time to change her clothes.

292
00:37:29,330 --> 00:37:31,620
- 你叫什么名字？ - 海蒂
- What is your name?  - Heidi.

293
00:37:31,790 --> 00:37:34,200
海蒂？那不是一个基督徒的名字
Heidi? That's not a Christian name.

294
00:37:34,500 --> 00:37:37,040
她叫艾迪尔海德，像她母亲
Her name is Adelheid, like her mother.

295
00:37:37,200 --> 00:37:38,450
上帝保佑她的灵魂
God rest her soul.

296
00:37:46,790 --> 00:37:49,240
孩子在我看来太小
The child seems very young to me.

297
00:37:49,410 --> 00:37:52,700
确实，对于她的年纪来说身体有点小
Indeed, she is quite small for her age.

298
00:37:52,870 --> 00:37:55,740
- 我八岁了  - 八岁
- I'm eight.  - Eight.

299
00:37:56,450 --> 00:37:59,700
不，这还不够，跟我过来，迪提
No, that won't do at all.Come with me, Dete.

300
00:38:05,700 --> 00:38:08,950
艾迪尔海德正是泽塞曼先生需要的
Adelheid is exactly what Mr Sesemann wanted.

301
00:38:09,120 --> 00:38:11,660
来自瑞士乡下的孩子
An unspoiled child from the Swiss countryside.

302
00:38:13,000 --> 00:38:15,080
现在给我的报酬吧
And now I want my side of the deal.

303
00:38:17,580 --> 00:38:20,540
- 我该叫你什么？ - 海蒂
- What should I call you?  - Heidi.

304
00:38:21,370 --> 00:38:22,910
我是克拉拉
I'm Klara.

305
00:38:24,000 --> 00:38:25,950
来法兰克福开心吗
Were you excited about Frankfurt?

306
00:38:27,330 --> 00:38:30,450
爷爷和迪提姑姑希望我来
Grandfather and Aunt Dete wanted me to come,

307
00:38:30,620 --> 00:38:33,870
但如果我不喜欢，我可以回去
but if I don't like it, I'm allowed to go back home.

308
00:38:34,500 --> 00:38:37,410
你是我见过最好奇的孩子
You're the most curious girl I've ever met.

309
00:38:38,580 --> 00:38:40,370
这是男孩子的衣服吗
Are those boys' clothes?

310
00:38:41,330 --> 00:38:44,660
在阿尔卑斯山区这很常见，尤其适合攀爬
It's practical on the alp.Especially for climbing.

311
00:38:45,750 --> 00:38:47,700
噢，攀爬
Oh, climbing...

312
00:38:50,250 --> 00:38:52,040
你不能走路吗？
Can't you walk?

313
00:38:52,200 --> 00:38:54,200
很不幸，不能
No, sadly not.

314
00:38:54,500 --> 00:38:57,370
- 所以你得坐在这上面？ - 是的
- So you always have to sit in this?  - Yes.

315
00:38:58,700 --> 00:38:59,740
随便推我走走吧
Feel free to push me.

316
00:39:05,830 --> 00:39:07,330
喜欢我们的房子吗
How do you like our house?

317
00:39:07,620 --> 00:39:08,830
好大
It's big.

318
00:39:12,000 --> 00:39:13,740
抱歉
I'm sorry.

319
00:39:20,910 --> 00:39:21,950
怎么了
What happened?

320
00:39:22,790 --> 00:39:26,700
我冲向了桌子，没注意，抱歉
I rode into the table. I wasn't paying attention. I'm sorry.

321
00:39:31,790 --> 00:39:35,040
好吧，晚饭时间到了
Right. It's time for supper.

322
00:39:37,080 --> 00:39:38,080
坐吧
Let's sit.

323
00:39:55,040 --> 00:39:58,200
你看起来像皮特一样的牧羊人
You look a bit like Peter the goatherd.

324
00:39:58,370 --> 00:40:00,540
- 请原谅  - 什么？
- Adelheid.  - Adelheid

325
00:40:00,830 --> 00:40:02,660
不要那样和仆人交谈
Don't talk like that to the servants.

326
00:40:10,500 --> 00:40:11,990
这间房子里我们用餐具
In this house we use cutlery.

327
00:40:13,910 --> 00:40:16,410
她不知道这些常识
She doesn't even know the very basics.

328
00:40:19,540 --> 00:40:21,950
抱歉，我去拿抹布
Sorry. I'll get a rag.

329
00:40:22,120 --> 00:40:23,410
抹布？
A rag?

330
00:40:23,700 --> 00:40:25,240
坐下，艾迪尔海德！
Sit down, Adelheid!

331
00:40:27,540 --> 00:40:30,040
蒂妮特，安静
Tinette. Silence!

332
00:40:46,250 --> 00:40:48,160
能给我两个吗？
Can I have two?

333
00:40:49,200 --> 00:40:50,990
塞巴斯蒂安
Sebastian.

334
00:40:51,290 --> 00:40:53,660
[纠正发音的问题]
他能给我两个面包卷吗？
"Can he please pass me two rolls?"

335
00:40:55,040 --> 00:40:59,120
他能给…我两个面包卷吗？
Can he please... give me two rolls?

336
00:41:00,370 --> 00:41:02,200
递给我两个面包卷
"Pass me two rolls."

337
00:41:03,750 --> 00:41:05,040
递给我两个面包卷
Pass me two rolls.

338
00:41:06,370 --> 00:41:08,410
两卷
Two rolls.

339
00:41:08,700 --> 00:41:11,080
两卷，请
Two rolls, please.

340
00:41:19,410 --> 00:41:22,040
艾迪尔海德，在这房子里有些规矩
In this house there are rules, Adelheid.

341
00:41:22,200 --> 00:41:25,830
提到仆人时你要说他或者她
You are to refer to the servants as 'he' or 'she',

342
00:41:26,000 --> 00:41:28,200
禁止与他们交谈
and conversing with them is forbidden.

343
00:41:30,410 --> 00:41:33,120
早餐是七点半
Breakfast is at 7:30.

344
00:41:33,290 --> 00:41:37,830
八点十五分开始上课
Lessons will take place in the study and commence at 8:15.

345
00:41:38,000 --> 00:41:40,950
十二点半午餐
At 12:30 we take our lunch.

346
00:41:41,870 --> 00:41:43,580
两小时午休
Then two hours of rest.

347
00:41:44,410 --> 00:41:45,700
晚上七点上床睡觉
At 7 it's bed time.

348
00:41:46,620 --> 00:41:49,870
房间里禁止奔跑，跳跃
In this house there is no running, hopping or jumping.

349
00:41:50,450 --> 00:41:52,200
我们一直步行
We always walk.

350
00:41:52,370 --> 00:41:54,450
从不大声说话
We never raise our voices.

351
00:41:54,620 --> 00:41:56,290
洛特梅尔小姐？
Miss Rottenmeier?

352
00:43:02,950 --> 00:43:04,580
你在干什么？
What are you doing?

353
00:43:09,250 --> 00:43:11,080
你不能像这样来回奔跑
You can't run around here like that.

354
00:43:11,250 --> 00:43:13,410
- 我？ - 是的！
- Me?  - Yes!

355
00:43:29,290 --> 00:43:31,540
山上的人都不洗澡吗？
Don't people wash up in the mountains?

356
00:43:32,540 --> 00:43:34,080
不，我们洗
Yes, we do.

357
00:43:37,160 --> 00:43:40,870
我听说在山上
I have heard that up there,

358
00:43:42,250 --> 00:43:45,120
有巨人和侏儒
there are mountain trolls and gnomes.

359
00:43:45,290 --> 00:43:47,120
你见过吗？
Have you ever seen one?

360
00:43:47,950 --> 00:43:49,450
别动
Stay still.

361
00:43:56,910 --> 00:44:00,950
穿上鞋子，准备好的话就上楼
Now put those on, and when you're ready, come upstairs.

362
00:44:18,830 --> 00:44:20,040
海蒂
Heidi!

363
00:44:34,370 --> 00:44:37,080
不，黄油刀
No, the butter knife.

364
00:44:46,250 --> 00:44:48,700
好的，艾迪尔海德小姐
Okay, Miss Adelheid.

365
00:44:49,870 --> 00:44:52,790
打开书本至第一章并朗读
Open the book at chapter one and read aloud.

366
00:45:04,450 --> 00:45:05,660
我不会
I can't.

367
00:45:06,580 --> 00:45:07,830
什么？
Pardon?

368
00:45:08,500 --> 00:45:10,200
我不会读
I can't read.

369
00:45:10,500 --> 00:45:12,410
你应该认识字母
You must know the letters.

370
00:45:15,700 --> 00:45:17,870
这是哪个字母？
Which letter is this?

371
00:45:18,450 --> 00:45:19,740
看起来像是座山
It's like a mountain.

372
00:45:21,410 --> 00:45:22,540
是的，它是
Yes, it is.

373
00:45:22,830 --> 00:45:24,660
克拉拉小姐，这不好笑
Miss Klara, this is not funny.

374
00:45:26,000 --> 00:45:27,700
皮特也不会读书
Peter can't read either.

375
00:45:27,870 --> 00:45:29,040
- 皮特？ - 皮特？
- Peter?  - Peter?

376
00:45:29,620 --> 00:45:31,490
他是我的朋友
He's my friend.

377
00:45:32,330 --> 00:45:34,950
皮特说我们山上不需要这个
Peter said we don't need to up on the alp.

378
00:45:35,250 --> 00:45:36,490
不需要？
