I'm only passing through,but I had to see you.

573
01:03:51,580 --> 01:03:53,450
让我看看你
Let me look at you.

574
01:03:53,620 --> 01:03:55,330
你看起来很好
You look very well!

575
01:03:56,370 --> 01:03:57,870
而且
And...

576
01:03:58,660 --> 01:04:00,790
日安，夫人
Good day, medeme.

577
01:04:01,080 --> 01:04:02,240
夫人
Madame.

578
01:04:02,540 --> 01:04:04,580
瞎说
Poppycock!

579
01:04:05,410 --> 01:04:06,870
叫我奶奶
Just call me Grandmama.

580
01:04:13,000 --> 01:04:15,870
我们幸运能找到一个克拉拉的朋友
We were right to find a friend for Klara.

581
01:04:16,410 --> 01:04:18,740
她好多了，很开心
She's much better, so cheerful.

582
01:04:19,580 --> 01:04:22,950
恐怕我的消息会让你失望
I'm afraid my news will dampen your spirits somewhat.

583
01:04:24,500 --> 01:04:27,200
在我看来，艾迪尔海德表现的…
In my opinion, Adelheid shows signs of...

584
01:04:28,450 --> 01:04:31,490
我没有办法教育好她
There's no other way for me to put it...

585
01:04:31,660 --> 01:04:33,330
她有点不对劲
...not being in her right mind.

586
01:04:35,450 --> 01:04:37,120
不对劲
Not in her right mind?

587
01:04:37,290 --> 01:04:40,290
- 什么意思  - 她不会朗读
- What do you mean?  - Adelheid still can't read.

588
01:04:41,700 --> 01:04:43,740
她甚至不认识字母
She can't even recognise the letters,

589
01:04:44,040 --> 01:04:47,330
即使教书先生尽他所能
even though Mr Kandidat is doing the very best he can.

590
01:04:50,000 --> 01:04:53,290
这严重影响了克拉拉小姐的学习
This is seriously disrupting Miss Klara's lessons.

591
01:04:53,830 --> 01:04:57,950
她的行为是不合适的，相当狂野
And her behaviour is impossible,downright wild.

592
01:04:58,830 --> 01:05:02,370
好吧，我得拿个主意了
Well, well.I'm going to make up my own mind.

593
01:05:03,410 --> 01:05:06,040
然后我们要对此负责
And then we'll take it from there.

594
01:05:14,660 --> 01:05:19,370
当年轻的牧羊人在晚上数他的羊时
"When the young shepherd counted his sheep in the evening,

595
01:05:19,540 --> 01:05:23,700
他发现最小的不见了
he realised that the smallest one was missing."

596
01:05:23,870 --> 01:05:25,240
去哪了呢？
"Where could it be?"

597
01:05:26,290 --> 01:05:29,740
外面开始下雪，刮起了寒风
"Outside it began to snow and an icy wind blew."

598
01:05:30,250 --> 01:05:32,790
我和皮特曾今遇到过这样的情况
That happened to me and Peter once.

599
01:05:32,950 --> 01:05:34,330
我们丢失了一只山羊
We lost a goat.

600
01:05:35,660 --> 01:05:39,040
- 后来找到了吗？ - 是的，谢天谢地
- Did you find it again?  - Yes. Thankfully.

601
01:05:40,080 --> 01:05:41,660
你从哪来
There, where you come from...

602
01:05:43,120 --> 01:05:46,990
我想一定和这里不同，我说的对吗？
I'm sure it's very different to here.Am I right?

603
01:05:56,120 --> 01:05:58,200
故事接下来怎么了
How does the story continue?

604
01:05:58,910 --> 01:06:00,830
请告诉我
Please.

605
01:06:01,120 --> 01:06:05,620
天越来越黑，雪花夹杂在空气中
"It got darker and darker and the snowflakes whirled through the air."

606
01:06:06,830 --> 01:06:08,830
但是突然
"But all of a sudden

607
01:06:09,750 --> 01:06:13,540
他听到了小羊的微弱心跳
he heard the very quiet bleating of a little sheep."

608
01:06:15,700 --> 01:06:19,450
好吧，我就读到这儿
Right, that's where I'm stopping.

609
01:06:21,410 --> 01:06:24,160
但是小羊，他找到了吗？
But the little sheep. Does he find it?

610
01:06:24,450 --> 01:06:26,830
你可以自己读这一段
You can read that for yourself.

611
01:06:27,580 --> 01:06:29,540
但我不会啊
But I can't.

612
01:06:29,830 --> 01:06:31,450
为什么不会呢
Why ever not?

613
01:06:32,870 --> 01:06:34,740
皮特说我们不需要朗读
Peter said we don't have to read.

614
01:06:35,910 --> 01:06:37,490
皮特说的，是吗？
Peter did, did he?

615
01:06:37,660 --> 01:06:41,620
你不能总是相信别人说的话
You don't always have to believe what other people say.

616
01:06:42,700 --> 01:06:47,410
如果你能够阅读，你会知道故事接下来的情节
If you could read you would know how the story continues.

617
01:06:50,870 --> 01:06:53,240
然后你会喜欢上这个故事，不是吗？
And you like stories, don't you?

618
01:06:53,410 --> 01:06:54,740
是的
Yes.

619
01:06:54,910 --> 01:06:56,410
那么，这样
Well, then.

620
01:06:57,500 --> 01:07:00,080
这本书我留给你
I'll leave the book there for you.

621
01:07:17,620 --> 01:07:22,910
海蒂是一个可爱并且极其敏感的孩子
Heidi is a sweet and incredibly sensitive child.

622
01:07:23,200 --> 01:07:26,910
我相信如果给予正确的引导她会学会阅读
I'm sure she can learn to read if given the right attention.

623
01:07:27,620 --> 01:07:29,330
太好了
Thank goodness for that.

624
01:07:29,620 --> 01:07:33,240
但是我想她的内心并不快乐
But I get the impression that she's not very happy.

625
01:07:34,500 --> 01:07:35,990
她应有尽有
She has all she could want.

626
01:07:36,580 --> 01:07:38,580
是内心深处的一些东西
It's something deep inside.

627
01:07:42,250 --> 01:07:45,870
住在这间屋子有违她的本性
Living in this house goes against everything she is.

628
01:07:48,290 --> 01:07:50,870
克拉拉从没有这么快乐
Klara has never been so happy.

629
01:07:51,040 --> 01:07:52,330
我知道
I see.

630
01:07:52,500 --> 01:07:56,990
同时它也让你对独自留下克拉拉不再感到愧疚
And it stops you feeling guilty about leaving Klara alone.

631
01:08:01,330 --> 01:08:02,910
胡说
Poppycock.

632
01:09:02,120 --> 01:09:03,620
嗯？
Hello?

633
01:09:08,080 --> 01:09:09,660
蒂妮特
Tinette.

634
01:09:11,290 --> 01:09:14,040
你在做什么，手里拿的什么
What are you doing?What's in your hand?

635
01:09:14,200 --> 01:09:15,910
有鬼，听到了吗？
A ghost! Don't you hear it?

636
01:09:16,200 --> 01:09:19,040
- 没有鬼这玩意  - 有，听
- There's no such thing as ghosts.  - There is! Listen.

637
01:09:32,330 --> 01:09:36,370
塞巴斯蒂安？救命啊，有鬼
Sebastian? Help! A ghost!

638
01:10:04,120 --> 01:10:05,490
没丢东西吧
Nothing was stolen?

639
01:10:05,660 --> 01:10:08,450
我亲自检查了银器三次
I checked the silver myself three times over.

640
01:10:08,620 --> 01:10:10,740
我锁了门
And I locked the door.

641
01:10:10,910 --> 01:10:12,410
我确定
I promise.

642
01:10:12,580 --> 01:10:15,040
肯定是鬼
It was a ghost, definitely.

643
01:10:15,200 --> 01:10:17,990
胡说，蒂妮特，荒唐
Poppycock, Tinette. What rot!

644
01:10:23,330 --> 01:10:26,700
塞巴斯蒂安，你是个聪明人，你肯定有答案
Sebastian, you're a sensible man. You must have an explanation.

645
01:10:27,000 --> 01:10:30,740
好吧，我必须承认
Well, I have to admit

646
01:10:30,910 --> 01:10:32,580
如果是主人问我
that if Sir is asking me,

647
01:10:32,750 --> 01:10:36,410
可以肯定的说事情发生的
then it certainly has to be said that things are happening,

648
01:10:36,580 --> 01:10:38,450
嗯
that, well...

649
01:10:39,790 --> 01:10:41,660
怎么说呢
that are somewhat, how shall I put it,

650
01:10:41,830 --> 01:10:43,700
事情变得有点灵异
that appear somewhat supernatural.

651
01:10:44,660 --> 01:10:47,160
- 灵异？ - 是的
- Supernatural?  - Yes.

652
01:10:47,330 --> 01:10:49,080
好吧，接下来
Right, then.

653
01:10:49,950 --> 01:10:51,540
嗯
Well...

654
01:10:52,700 --> 01:10:55,830
我会制止这些愚蠢的行动
I'm going to put a stop to all these carryings-on.

655
01:10:57,370 --> 01:11:01,160
不要让孩子们听到任何关于这件事的消息
Please make sure that the children hear nothing about this.

656
01:11:02,450 --> 01:11:03,990
晚安
Goodnight.

657
01:11:05,540 --> 01:11:07,290
- 睡觉吧  - 晚安
- To bed.  - Goodnight.

658
01:11:28,870 --> 01:11:33,540
在
In... the...

659
01:11:39,040 --> 01:11:41,370
山
vall...

660
01:11:41,540 --> 01:11:42,950
谷里
ey...

661
01:11:43,120 --> 01:11:45,330
在山谷里
"In the valley."

662
01:11:45,620 --> 01:11:48,700
在山谷里，有条
"In the valley, there flowed

663
01:11:49,790 --> 01:11:53,870
小溪流淌着
a small stream

664
01:11:54,040 --> 01:11:57,080
在澄净的水里
and in the clear water

665
01:11:57,250 --> 01:12:00,290
能看到鳟鱼在游动
you could see the trout swimming."

666
01:12:00,450 --> 01:12:02,870
好样的，海蒂，我就知道你办得到
Yes! Heidi, I knew you could do it.

667
01:12:03,160 --> 01:12:04,540
- 我就知道  - 太好了
- I knew it.  - Superb.

668
01:12:09,450 --> 01:12:10,790
谁能想得到？
Who would have thought it?

669
01:12:11,250 --> 01:12:15,160
鱼多的使小河看起来银光闪闪
"The fish glittered silver,

670
01:12:15,330 --> 01:12:20,080
鱼儿们嬉闹着前进
and frolicked around playfully."

671
01:12:20,540 --> 01:12:25,490
在这个美丽的地方
"Here at this lov... lovely place,

672
01:12:25,660 --> 01:12:28,410
牧羊人想休息一下
the shepherd wanted to rest

673
01:12:28,700 --> 01:12:32,870
吃完他的午餐
and eat his midday meal."

674
01:12:33,040 --> 01:12:34,370
好样的，她做到了
Yes, she can do it!

675
01:12:34,660 --> 01:12:37,740
- 我太高兴了，奶奶  - 好样的，海蒂
- I'm so pleased, Grandmama.  - Bravo, bravo, Heidi!

676
01:12:41,290 --> 01:12:45,540
每个孩子都能学会朗读只有有个好老师和一些耐心
Every child can learn to read with a good teacher and some patience.

677
01:12:45,700 --> 01:12:49,870
海蒂，我很高心
Heidi, I'm delighted.

678
01:12:50,700 --> 01:12:53,660
我们的小瑞士女孩看起来做的很好
Our little Swiss girl seems to be doing well here.

679
01:12:55,450 --> 01:12:57,290
这也是为什么
And that's why...

680
01:12:59,790 --> 01:13:01,450
她能够和我们待在一起
she should stay with us.

681
01:13:01,620 --> 01:13:03,290
- 永远？ - 是的
- Forever?  - Yes.

682
01:13:04,790 --> 01:13:06,450
是的，我的孩子，永远
Yes, my child, forever.

683
01:13:43,950 --> 01:13:45,870
- 再见，母亲  - 再见
- Goodbye, Mother.  - Goodbye.

684
01:13:47,040 --> 01:13:48,950
驾…
Giddy up!

685
01:14:29,540 --> 01:14:31,490
你能待多久，我的朋友
How long can you stay, friend?

686
01:14:32,750 --> 01:14:35,830
生意一结束我就得离开
I'll leave as soon as this business is cleared up.

687
01:14:37,870 --> 01:14:40,370
今晚我希望能亲眼见到鬼魂
I hope to see the ghost for myself tonight.

688
01:14:41,580 --> 01:14:43,450
我的第一次啊
It would be my first.

689
01:15:28,370 --> 01:15:29,410
孩子！
Child!

690
01:15:31,790 --> 01:15:34,990
你到底在干什么？
What on earth are you doing here?

691
01:15:35,870 --> 01:15:39,200
不要碰她，你不应该弄醒梦游者
Don't touch her!You shouldn't wake sleepwalkers.

692
01:16:13,500 --> 01:16:14,790
她快冻僵了
She's freezing cold.

693
01:16:15,080 --> 01:16:17,580
能再拿条毯子来吗？
Could you bring another blanket?

694
01:16:24,830 --> 01:16:26,870
地上是什么
What on earth...

695
01:16:31,370 --> 01:16:32,580
给
Here.

696
01:16:32,750 --> 01:16:34,740
让我们两单独待在一起
Please leave us two alone.

697
01:16:43,200 --> 01:16:44,490
不要害怕，海蒂
Don't be scared, Heidi.

698
01:16:45,950 --> 01:16:48,160
是我，那个医生
It's me, the doctor.

699
01:16:50,410 --> 01:16:52,740
你梦到了什么
Were you dreaming?

700
01:16:54,450 --> 01:16:56,700
爷爷
About Grandfather.

701
01:16:58,950 --> 01:17:00,790
你哪里不舒服？
Are you in any pain?

702
01:17:01,080 --> 01:17:03,580
只有这里
No, only here.

703
01:17:03,750 --> 01:17:05,620
好疼
This hurts.

704
01:17:07,870 --> 01:17:11,870
亲爱的孩子，你为什么存着这些面包卷
My dear child,why did you save all those bread rolls?

705
01:17:12,160 --> 01:17:17,120
它们是为奶奶准备的，她不能吃硬面包
They're for Grandmother.She can't eat hard bread anymore.

706
01:17:22,120 --> 01:17:24,620
你想家了，小海蒂
You miss your home, little Heidi.

707
01:17:35,580 --> 01:17:36,990
来！
Come on.

708
01:17:38,330 --> 01:17:39,950
这里
There, there.

709
01:17:40,250 --> 01:17:42,240
会好起来的
Everything will be okay.

710
01:17:49,660 --> 01:17:51,160
思乡病？
Homesick, you say?

711
01:17:51,330 --> 01:17:54,120
女孩病了，她从来没有平静过
The Swiss illness.Her nerves are in quite a state.

712
01:17:54,290 --> 01:17:57,160
要立刻送她回去
She must be sent home immediately.

713
01:17:57,330 --> 01:17:59,830
- 不行  - 必须送她走
- She can't.  - She must!

714
01:18:03,660 --> 01:18:06,080
我不能这样对克拉拉
I can't do that to Klara. Please.

715
01:18:06,250 --> 01:18:08,200
尽你所能，好吗？
Do all you can, okay?

716
01:18:10,250 --> 01:18:11,660
我已经给出了我的建议
I've given you my advice.

717
01:18:40,200 --> 01:18:41,910
你看到了鬼魂吗？
So? Did you see the ghost?

718
01:18:43,870 --> 01:18:45,040
我什么也没说
I didn't say anything.

719
01:18:45,330 --> 01:18:47,700
告诉我一切，爸爸
Tell me everything, Father. Please!

720
01:18:49,620 --> 01:18:51,200
克拉拉
Klara.

721
01:18:52,290 --> 01:18:53,450
鬼魂
The ghost...

722
01:18:54,500 --> 01:18:55,950
是我们的小海蒂
was our little Heidi.

723
01:18:56,250 --> 01:18:57,290
海蒂？
-Heidi?

724
01:18:57,580 --> 01:18:59,990
因为痛苦她梦游
She sleepwalks because she's suffering.

725
01:19:01,040 --> 01:19:03,660
- 她需要什么  - 她的家
- What does she need?  - Her home.

726
01:19:07,290 --> 01:19:10,290
所以，亲爱的，海蒂不能待在这里了
So, my dear child, Heidi cannot stay here.

727
01:19:10,450 --> 01:19:12,830
但是她应该，你不能这样做
But she has to.You can't do that!

728
01:19:13,500 --> 01:19:16,290
请不要这样，没有海蒂我该怎么办
Please don't! What will I do without Heidi?

729
01:19:16,450 --> 01:19:20,330
- 海蒂病了，如果想治愈只能…  - 我要她留在这儿
- Heidi's illness will only be cured...  - I want her to stay here!

730
01:19:20,950 --> 01:19:23,330
- 我也病了而且一直独自一人  - 克拉拉
- I'm sick and all alone too!  - Klara.

731
01:19:25,620 --> 01:19:29,160
你失控了，冷静下来
You're forgetting yourself.Calm down this instant!

732
01:19:32,000 --> 01:19:32,990
走吧
Just go!

733
01:19:33,290 --> 01:19:35,990
去找你的爷爷和皮特，所有人，走吧
Go to your grandfather and Peter.Everyone, just leave!

734
01:19:40,120 --> 01:19:42,410
蒂妮特，送我回房间
Tinette, take me to my room right away.

735
01:19:50,870 --> 01:19:51,950
艾迪尔海德
Adelheid.

736
01:19:58,200 --> 01:19:59,990
塞巴斯蒂安今天会送你回家
Sebastian will take you home today.

737
01:20:00,580 --> 01:20:04,540
中午你会去坐火车，蒂妮特会帮你整理行李
You'll take the train at midday.Tinette will help you pack.

738
01:20:04,700 --> 01:20:06,120
回爷爷家？
Home to Grandfather?

739
01:20:11,830 --> 01:20:13,580
克拉拉呢？
And Klara?

740
01:20:25,790 --> 01:20:27,160
克拉拉？在吗？
Klara?

741
01:20:34,290 --> 01:20:35,410
克拉拉
Klara.

742
01:20:36,620 --> 01:20:38,160
开门好吗
Please open the door.

743
01:21:08,500 --> 01:21:10,200
谢谢
Thank you.

744
01:21:16,660 --> 01:21:18,790
能把这个交给克拉拉吗？
Can you give this to Klara?

745
01:21:22,750 --> 01:21:25,490
她应该来看我
She has to come and visit me.

746
01:21:25,660 --> 01:21:26,790
拜托
Please.

747
01:21:30,200 --> 01:21:31,620
再见
We'll see.

748
01:21:48,410 --> 01:21:49,830
驾
Giddy up.

749
01:21:51,370 --> 01:21:52,700
走你
Off you go!

750
01:21:59,410 --> 01:22:01,990
终于又重归平静
Peace again at last.

751
01:22:14,870 --> 01:22:17,120
蒂妮特，蒂妮特
Tinette! Tinette!

752
01:22:23,580 --> 01:22:26,080
就叫你海蒂吧
I'll call you Heidi.

753
01:22:27,040 --> 01:22:28,160
我的小海蒂
My little Heidi.

754
01:22:36,750 --> 01:22:38,040
再见
Goodbye.

755
01:22:43,910 --> 01:22:45,990
人们住在这儿
People live up there...

756
01:22:47,250 --> 01:22:50,490
那些山，如此的压抑
Those mountains! It's so oppressive.

757
01:22:59,120 --> 01:23:01,040
来！
Come here.

758
01:23:01,330 --> 01:23:04,200
非常荣幸，小姐
It has been a great pleasure, miss.

759
01:23:07,500 --> 01:23:09,620
- 照看好孩子  - 会的
- Look affer the child well.  - I will.

760
01:23:14,540 --> 01:23:15,580
再见
Adieu!

761
01:23:24,450 --> 01:23:26,950
- 看  - 这是谁？
- Hey, look!  - What is it?

762
01:23:27,250 --> 01:23:28,740
她是海蒂
That's Heidi.

763
01:23:29,040 --> 01:23:31,040
你好，海蒂
Hello, Heidi.

764
01:23:31,540 --> 01:23:32,830
来
Come!

765
01:23:33,120 --> 01:23:34,580
太好了，我要那个
Nice! I want that!

766
01:23:35,200 --> 01:23:36,370
看看这些鞋子
Look at these shoes.

767
01:23:38,080 --> 01:23:40,200
- 海蒂  - 皮特
- Heidi!  - Peter!

768
01:23:47,580 --> 01:23:52,450
- 海蒂，我听说你住在个宫殿里  - 不是宫殿
- Heidi, I heard you lived in a palace.  - It wasn't a palace.

769
01:23:54,250 --> 01:23:57,080
- 里面是什么  - 马上就知道了
- What is in there?  - Wait and see.

770
01:24:06,000 --> 01:24:09,120
这些是给你的，奶奶，很多软面包
These are for you, Grandmother. Lots of soft rolls.

771
01:24:09,290 --> 01:24:11,080
你回来太好了，海蒂
It's lovely you're back, Heidi.

772
01:24:14,660 --> 01:24:16,330
给你的大香肠，皮特
A big sausage for you, Peter.

773
01:24:16,790 --> 01:24:17,830
谢谢
Thank you.

774
01:24:34,000 --> 01:24:44,490
爷爷
Grandfather!

775
01:24:59,500 --> 01:25:01,200
海蒂
Heidi!

776
01:25:32,580 --> 01:25:34,740
早上好，小天鹅与小熊[山羊名]
Morning, Little Swan and Little Bear.

777
01:25:35,750 --> 01:25:37,490
皮特，我来了
Peter, I'm coming!

778
01:25:46,330 --> 01:25:47,490
不
No!

779
01:25:52,620 --> 01:25:56,330
- 给，你的一半  - 谢谢
- So, here's your half.  - Thank you.

780
01:26:25,500 --> 01:26:26,540
亲爱的克拉拉
Dear Klara,

781
01:26:27,700 --> 01:26:30,240
村子现在被厚厚的大雪覆盖
the village is now under thick snow.

782
01:26:30,540 --> 01:26:34,120
所有东西都是白的并且闪闪发亮
Everything is white and sparkling.

783
01:26:36,410 --> 01:26:38,450
我们被迫搬到村子里住
We have moved into the village

784
01:26:38,620 --> 01:26:40,620
所以我可以去上学了
so that I can go to school.

785
01:26:42,910 --> 01:26:46,870
在学校，男孩坐在一边，女孩们坐在另一边
At school, boys sit on one side and girls on the other.

786
01:26:48,040 --> 01:26:50,830
我们的牧师比教书先生还严厉
Our pastor is much stricter than Mr Kandidat.

787
01:26:51,120 --> 01:26:53,370
有时甚至会鞭笞学生
Sometimes there are even canings.

788
01:26:53,540 --> 01:26:58,080
可怜的皮特nal由于迟到经常被惩罚
And poor Peter is always punished because he's always late.

789
01:26:58,250 --> 01:27:01,410
现在告诉我长大后你想干什么
Now tell me what you want to be when you grow up.

790
01:27:02,330 --> 01:27:03,790
牧羊人
A goatherd.

791
01:27:07,830 --> 01:27:10,120
- 农民  - 农民
- A farmer.  - Farmer.

792
01:27:12,790 --> 01:27:14,910
铁匠，像我父亲一样
A blacksmith. Like my father.

793
01:27:15,080 --> 01:27:16,580
铁匠
Blacksmith.

794
01:27:25,200 --> 01:27:26,790
我想写故事
I want to write stories.

795
01:27:27,750 --> 01:27:29,240
安静
Ouiet!

796
01:27:29,410 --> 01:27:31,080
我知道了
I see.

797
01:27:31,370 --> 01:27:32,580
这个字母是？
What letter is this?

798
01:27:32,870 --> 01:27:35,240
- “A”？ - 这是“D”
- 'A'?  - A letter 'D'!

799
01:27:35,410 --> 01:27:38,240
几乎每天放学后
Almost every day after school,

800
01:27:38,540 --> 01:27:40,580
我都要教皮特朗读
I try to teach poor Peter to read.

801
01:27:40,750 --> 01:27:42,950
皮特，昨天刚学过啊
Oh Peter, you did this yesterday.

802
01:27:43,120 --> 01:27:45,160
现在就不会了
But it's not really working.

803
01:27:57,620 --> 01:28:00,740
克拉拉，我想你了
Oh Klara, I miss you so much.

804
01:28:00,910 --> 01:28:02,830
我每天都在想你
I think about you every day.

805
01:28:04,080 --> 01:28:05,410
请给我写信
Please write to me.

806
01:28:06,500 --> 01:28:11,490
我最期待的是你能来看我
"There's nothing I wish for more than for you to come and visit me."

807
01:28:13,750 --> 01:28:15,370
你的，海蒂
"Yours, Heidi."

808
01:28:16,750 --> 01:28:18,870
我甚至没有说再见
I didn't even say goodbye.

809
01:28:53,290 --> 01:28:56,450
我的天啊！我的天啊，是克拉拉
I don't believe it. I don't believe it. It's Klara!

810
01:28:56,620 --> 01:29:00,290
皮特，皮特，皮特！
Peter, Peter, Peter!

811
01:29:00,580 --> 01:29:04,870
皮特，看，是克拉拉，我最亲爱的朋友，克拉拉
Peter, look! It's Klara.My dearest friend! Klara!

812
01:29:11,540 --> 01:29:12,660
- 克拉拉  - 海蒂
- Klara!  - Heidi!

813
01:29:15,580 --> 01:29:18,790
- 海蒂，我太想你了  - 我也想你
- Heidi, I missed you so much.  - I missed you too.

814
01:29:20,370 --> 01:29:23,660
- 奶奶  - 海蒂
- Grandmama!  - Heidi!

815
01:29:25,330 --> 01:29:28,660
我的乖孩子
My dear child.

816
01:29:56,790 --> 01:30:00,040
看，克拉拉的情况相当糟糕
You see, Klara was in such an awful way,

817
01:30:00,200 --> 01:30:03,040
我决定带她来这里
I resolved to bring her here.

818
01:30:04,750 --> 01:30:08,700
她能在这里待一段时间吗？
Do you think she could stay here for a few days?

819
01:30:08,870 --> 01:30:11,580
当然，会付钱的
For a fee, of course.

820
01:30:13,120 --> 01:30:15,450
克拉拉是我们的客人
Klara is our guest.

821
01:30:38,700 --> 01:30:41,290
- 好的  - 确定？
- Okay.  - Sure?

822
01:30:59,200 --> 01:31:00,330
海蒂
Heidi!

823
01:31:13,040 --> 01:31:16,040
海蒂，你得帮我穿衣服
Heidi, you have to help me get dressed.

824
01:31:23,370 --> 01:31:26,290
- 你不需要这个  - 海蒂
- You don't need this.  - Heidi!

825
01:31:27,290 --> 01:31:29,240
一件也不需要
Or any of this either.

826
01:31:29,540 --> 01:31:31,370
看，我也不需要它们
Look.I don't need them either.

827
01:31:40,910 --> 01:31:43,120
海蒂，不要太快
Heidi, not so fast.

828
01:31:45,250 --> 01:31:46,620
小熊、小天鹅[山羊名]
Little Bear, Little Swan.

829
01:31:51,120 --> 01:31:52,910
它们和我想的一样
They're just like I imagined.

830
01:31:54,200 --> 01:31:56,290
皮特，过来啊
Peter, come!

831
01:31:58,950 --> 01:32:01,660
皮特，看，这是克拉拉
Peter, look. It's Klara.

832
01:32:03,790 --> 01:32:05,830
克拉拉，这是皮特
Klara, this is Peter.

833
01:32:06,120 --> 01:32:07,990
你好，百闻不如一见
Hello.I've heard so much about you.

834
01:32:09,040 --> 01:32:10,450
你来吗？
Are you coming?

835
01:32:12,290 --> 01:32:14,990
- 不  - 为什么，让我们和他一起去
- No.  - Why? Let's go with him.

836
01:32:15,160 --> 01:32:17,540
怎么可能，你无法走路
How will that work?You can't walk.

837
01:32:17,830 --> 01:32:20,450
- 皮特  - 来吧，我们走
- Peter!  - Come on, let's go.

838
01:32:20,750 --> 01:32:22,830
我不会留下克拉拉独自一人
I'm not leaving Klara on her own.

839
01:32:31,160 --> 01:32:32,330
- 快走  - 皮特
- Move, go!  - Peter!

840
01:32:32,870 --> 01:32:34,330
他会熬过去的
He'll get over it.

841
01:32:34,620 --> 01:32:37,490
我们走，动起来
We're going! Move!

842
01:32:37,660 --> 01:32:41,040
海蒂，我想和你们两个一起上山去
Heidi,I'd love to go up there with you two.

843
01:33:26,450 --> 01:33:27,580
快点走
Come on! Move!

844
01:33:30,040 --> 01:33:31,410
走
Move!

845
01:33:42,830 --> 01:33:44,240
自己回家去吧
Go home on your own.

846
01:33:44,540 --> 01:33:46,080
你们这些愚蠢的山羊
You stupid bunch of goats.

847
01:33:46,370 --> 01:33:49,910
走吧，一个跟一个
Come on, get a move on! Go!

848
01:33:56,160 --> 01:33:59,160
- 看到了吗  - 星星在闪耀
- Did you see that?  - Yes, a shooting star.

849
01:33:59,330 --> 01:34:01,200
现在让我们许愿吧
Now we can wish for something.

850
01:34:03,410 --> 01:34:04,990
- 我希望…  - 不
- I wish that…  - No!

851
01:34:06,200 --> 01:34:07,870
不要说出来
You're not allowed to say.

852
01:35:20,290 --> 01:35:21,330
该死的
Damn!

853
01:35:25,000 --> 01:35:26,580
走吧，山羊
Come on, goats!

854
01:35:45,500 --> 01:35:48,740
轮椅在哪儿，海蒂，轮椅去哪了
Where is the wheelchair? Heidi, where is it?

855
01:35:52,290 --> 01:35:53,830
不在这儿
It's not here.

856
01:35:56,660 --> 01:35:58,580
也不在这儿
It's not here either.

857
01:36:00,120 --> 01:36:02,120
它不可能这样消失
It can't just disappear.

858
01:36:03,620 --> 01:36:06,910
- 爷爷，它不见了  - 什么？轮椅不见了
- Grandfather, it's not here.  - What? It's gone?

859
01:36:08,040 --> 01:36:10,540
不可能，你四处找过了吗
Impossible.Did you look everywhere?

860
01:36:11,080 --> 01:36:14,330
现在我得在这儿坐一整天什么也干不了
Now I have to sit here all day and can't do anything.

861
01:36:14,500 --> 01:36:17,240
爷爷会想出办法的
Grandfather will think of something.

862
01:36:20,450 --> 01:36:22,660
我要好好教训他一顿
He'll be getting a piece of my mind.

863
01:36:51,580 --> 01:36:52,870
小熊[山羊名]
Little Bear?

864
01:37:06,620 --> 01:37:08,410
谢谢你
Thank you.

865
01:37:09,500 --> 01:37:10,830
待在这儿
There you go.

866
01:37:23,250 --> 01:37:26,410
我知道你做了什么，小子
I know what you did, General Goatherd.

867
01:37:27,790 --> 01:37:31,160
你的坏行为会受到惩罚的
Your bad conscience is probably punishment enough.

868
01:37:35,950 --> 01:37:40,620
在我晚上回来前好好照看女孩们
Now look affer the girls until I come back in the evening.

869
01:37:41,700 --> 01:37:43,200
懂我的意思吗？
Do you understand me?

870
01:37:51,790 --> 01:37:54,200
- 我去找皮特  - 好的，去吧
- I'll go and get Peter.  - Yes, do.

871
01:38:03,450 --> 01:38:04,540
出来
Come out.

872
01:38:07,370 --> 01:38:09,040
不要
I don't want to.

873
01:38:10,160 --> 01:38:11,740
那好吧
Then don't.

874
01:38:12,040 --> 01:38:15,200
只要这儿有吃的他就会马上出来
He'll come for sure. As soon as there's food.

875
01:38:16,290 --> 01:38:17,990
好美
They're beautiful.

876
01:38:18,620 --> 01:38:22,450
- 就像你说的  - 看吧，你现在就在这里
- It's just like you said.  - See? And now you're here.

877
01:38:26,540 --> 01:38:27,910
我去采点蓝莓
I'll fetch some blueberries.

878
01:39:12,660 --> 01:39:14,620
克拉拉
Klara!

879
01:39:22,540 --> 01:39:24,290
我的天啊
Holy Mother of God.

880
01:39:30,660 --> 01:39:31,910
快点过来
Come over here!

881
01:39:40,080 --> 01:39:41,200
来
Come on.

882
01:39:41,370 --> 01:39:43,330
你行的
You can do it.

883
01:39:55,450 --> 01:39:56,660
试试
Try it.

884
01:39:59,000 --> 01:40:00,040
我知道你可以的
I know you can do it!

885
01:40:29,040 --> 01:40:30,580
日安
Good day.

886
01:40:33,580 --> 01:40:35,790
我来接我的女儿
I'm here to collect my daughter.

887
01:40:35,950 --> 01:40:38,870
- 你好，阿蒙治叔叔  - 你好
- Hello Alp-Uncle.  - Hello.

888
01:40:42,250 --> 01:40:46,700
母亲，你怎么能带克拉拉来这样一个地方
Mother, how could you bring Klara to a place like this?

889
01:40:46,870 --> 01:40:48,200
看看
Just look at it!

890
01:40:48,500 --> 01:40:50,660
这不适合生病的女孩
This is no place for a sick girl.

891
01:40:50,830 --> 01:40:53,830
这间小屋，这些怪石嶙峋
This hut, these rocks everywhere.

892
01:40:54,000 --> 01:40:55,660
你必须道歉，儿子
You must excuse my son.

893
01:40:55,830 --> 01:40:58,790
我现在要见我的女儿，她在哪儿
I want to see my daughter right away.Where is she?

894
01:40:58,950 --> 01:41:01,410
爸爸，我在这里
Father, here I am.

895
01:41:05,700 --> 01:41:06,740
克拉拉
Klara.

896
01:41:20,410 --> 01:41:22,410
爸爸
Father.

897
01:41:24,950 --> 01:41:26,290
我的孩子
My child.

898
01:41:27,830 --> 01:41:29,410
你能走路了
You're walking.

899
01:41:33,750 --> 01:41:35,950
请原谅我
Please forgive me.

900
01:41:36,870 --> 01:41:38,620
爸爸
Father.

901
01:41:44,290 --> 01:41:46,450
- 你能走路了  - 克拉拉
- You're walking.  - Klara.

902
01:41:56,160 --> 01:41:59,040
我的孩子，这是给你的礼物
This is a present for you,my dear child.

903
01:42:00,950 --> 01:42:02,120
谢谢你，奶奶
Thank you, Grandmama.

904
01:42:10,790 --> 01:42:12,120
里面什么也没有啊
There's nothing in it.

905
01:42:12,790 --> 01:42:15,660
你得自己把它填满
Because you'll fill it up yourself.

906
01:42:21,660 --> 01:42:23,160
怎么了，孩子
What's wrong, child?

907
01:42:23,660 --> 01:42:26,700
- 人们嘲笑我  - 为什么呢
- Everyone laughed at me.  - Why is that?

908
01:42:28,290 --> 01:42:30,370
因为我想写故事
Because I want to write stories.

909
01:42:31,250 --> 01:42:33,080
是吗
Is that right?

910
01:42:34,660 --> 01:42:37,660
他们鼠目寸光，海蒂
They just don't know any better, Heidi,

911
01:42:37,830 --> 01:42:39,740
因为他们只知道这个村子
because they only know this village.

912
01:42:40,750 --> 01:42:44,540
但是你已经见识过外面的世界了，不是吗？
But you've seen more of the world,haven't you?

913
01:42:47,040 --> 01:42:49,830
如果生活中的某件事情带给你快乐
If something in life brings you joy,

914
01:42:50,120 --> 01:42:52,450
你只需要去做它就行
then you simply have to do it,

915
01:42:52,620 --> 01:42:54,540
不要管别人说什么
regardless of what people say.

916
01:43:03,330 --> 01:43:05,450
能见到你太好了
It was so lovely to see you.

917
01:43:07,370 --> 01:43:08,870
我会想你的
I'll miss you.

918
01:43:09,040 --> 01:43:10,370
我也会想你的
I'll miss you too.

919
01:43:19,870 --> 01:43:23,370
再见
Goodbye.

920
01:43:25,080 --> 01:43:26,830
海蒂，再见
Heidi, goodbye.

921
01:43:29,500 --> 01:43:30,620
再见
Adieu!

